rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_SEL0011
rows.name:
Ask Loda about his thoughts on
friendship treaties with xenoforms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Loda if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Loda about the Ganglion attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_SEL1041
rows.name: Ask Loda about the Ganglion attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Loda if anything is troubling him.

rows.label: tev042001_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Loda about the Cavern Clan.

rows.label: tev042001_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Loda if anything is troubling him.

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0001
rows.name: You saved my family. I am grateful. But know this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0002
rows.name:
Our treaty makes Earth aliens equal to Prone.
Not better.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0003
rows.name:
We are not Cavern Clan.
No alien will keep us beneath boot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0004
rows.name:
Do not insult pride of Tree Clan.
Or you will pay with life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0005
rows.name: I hope you hear me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0008
rows.name: Do you know father's pain, Earth alien?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0009
rows.name: My daughter, Lavina, has reached marrying age.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0010
rows.name:
I worry her mate will be that ridiculous Earth alien!
I cannot bear such thoughts![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0011
rows.name:
But I cannot keep her safe forever.
She must become mother and pillar of Tree Clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0012
rows.name:
Maybe I can give her to warrior like Wazdo Tygant?
Ugh. What to do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0013
rows.name: Cavern Clan fought for Ganglion during attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0014
rows.name:
If Tree Clan had been in city, we would have faced
those cowards. You could not have stopped us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0015
rows.name:
City streets would have been final battleground for
struggle of 10,000 suns! Ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0016
rows.name:
We do not fear death in strange world.
So long as we take Cavern Clan with us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0020
rows.name: Because of you, I now have Earth-alien family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0021
rows.name:
Leroy is stronger than I thought.
When I give him punishment, he takes it like man.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0022
rows.name: He might not be such bad match for my daughter...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0023
rows.name:
But I still do not accept him! Not yet.
He must prove he can keep Lavina safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0024
rows.name:
Given time, I will whip him into shape.
If he is lucky, I will not use real whip! Ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0035
rows.name: Cavern Clan fought for Ganglion during attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0036
rows.name:
You should have let me borrow Skell.
I would have stopped them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0037
rows.name:
My strength! Your metal weapon!
We would have ended them for good![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0038
rows.name:
...Hmm? I would not fit in "cockpit"?
Isn't Skell just big suit of armor?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG1001
rows.name:
Leader of Ganglion has fallen.
But survivors still roam Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG1002
rows.name:
If I was younger, I would find Cavern Clan cowards.
End long quarrel for good![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG1003
rows.name:
But I am not young. I am old and weak.
So you must punish what remains.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0025
rows.name:
My daughter waits for Leroy to return.
Waits without complaint.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0026
rows.name:
It seems Lavina is no longer little girl.
She is fine Prone woman! Ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0027
rows.name: And I was wrong about Leroy. He is brave.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0028
rows.name: I think he will return as stronger husband.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev042001_MSG0029
rows.name: But I will still complain about him! That is father's right.[ST:wait ]
